The error is that you're trying to print "selected.score", but in the defin
definition of 'selected', only the field "points" is defined, not "score". 
You need to change this line from 
```tundra
print(selected.score);
```
to
```tundra
print(selected.points);
```
The correct program will be:
```tundra
val raw = {
  profile: {
    name: "Ada",
    score: 12
   }
};

val profile = raw.profile;
val selected = {
  points: profile.score
};

print(selected.points);
```
